<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container footer__grid">
    <div class="footer__brand">
      <a href="/" aria-label="DaisyWoont.nl home">
        <img src="/images/Frame-233.svg" alt="DaisyWoont.nl logo" width="103" height="33" />
      </a>
      <p>
        Het team van DaisyWoont.nl deelt hun inzichten op het gebied van wonen met jou. Doe je
        inspiratie op door de top 10 lijstjes per type interieur te bekijken.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer__col">
      <h3>Informatie</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog/">Blogs</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#over-ons">Over ons</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact/">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="footer__col">
      <h3>Categorieën</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/#services">Meubilair</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#services">Verwarmers &amp; Koelers</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#services">Wassen &amp; Drogen</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#services">Badkamer</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="footer__col">
      <h3>Andere Daisy sites</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://lifestyledaisy.nl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LifestyleDaisy.nl</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer__bottom">
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; 2026 All rights reserved — DaisyWoont.nl</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    padding-top: 3rem;
  }

  .footer__grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .footer__brand p {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    max-width: 320px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  }

  .footer__col h3 {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .footer__col ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .footer__col a {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    transition: color var(--transition);
  }

  .footer__col a:hover {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .footer__bottom {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding-block: 1.25rem;
  }

  .footer__bottom p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .footer__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
